    <h1>Gateway of India</h1>
    <p>An Iconic Symbol of Mumbai's Rich Heritage and Maritime History</p>
</div>


<div class="content">
   
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582477795644-d2b3348c0e75?q=80&w=2060&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Gateway of India">
